[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1m[Detected habits]  (by catalog ID, most frequent first)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[33m  [H5-04] \u001b[0m\u001b[1mInviting verbose output\u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Г—15\u001b[0m\r\n  est. waste: ~12,000 tokens\r\n\u001b[2m  fix: \u001b[0mCap the output: \"in 2 lines\", \"no code or examples\". Set response defaults in CLAUDE.md.\r\n\r\n\u001b[33m  [H2-01] \u001b[0m\u001b[1mRe-reading the same file\u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Г—8\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  est. waste: ~16,000 tokens\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m  fix: \u001b[0mReference what you already read (\"from the X you read earlier...\") instead of re-Reading. Block it with a PreToolUse hook.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[33m  [H2-04] \u001b[0m\u001b[1mStranded web results (WebFetch/WebSearch)\u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Г—8\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  frequency signal вЂ” not scored (8 calls; check context)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  fix: \u001b[0mDelegate research to a subagent so only the summary returns. Don't re-fetch the same page; narrow your queries.\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[33m  [H1-01] \u001b[0m\u001b[1mTopic drift / marathon session\u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Г—2\u001b[0m\r\n  est. waste: ~20,000 tokens\r\n\u001b[2m  fix: \u001b[0mAt ~35 min / ~50K tokens, /compact or /clear and start a fresh session.\r\n\r\n\u001b[33m  [H1-03] \u001b[0m\u001b[1mCompaction overrun (token pile-up)\u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Г—2\u001b[0m\r\n  est. waste: ~30,000 tokens\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m  fix: \u001b[0mRun /compact [focus] manually before you hit ~50K tokens.\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[33m  [H2-02] \u001b[0m\u001b[1mDumping full logs / stdout flood\u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Г—1\u001b[0m\r\n  est. waste: ~5,100 tokens\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m  fix: \u001b[0mFilter before running: pipe through grep -A5 'FAIL|ERROR' or | head -50. Save to a file and pass the path.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[33m  [H4-03] \u001b[0m\u001b[1mCache-kill switch (cache hit-rate crash)\u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Г—1\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  est. waste: ~21,000 tokens\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m  fix: \u001b[0mAvoid switching model/effort mid-session. Open a new session when you must switch.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[33m  [H8-01] \u001b[0m\u001b[1mMain-thread exploration (many Reads in one turn)\u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Г—1\u001b[0m\r\n  est. waste: ~5,000 tokens\r\n\u001b[2m  fix: \u001b[0mDelegate exploration to a subagent: \"search src/auth/ and return only function names + locations.\"\r\n\r\n\u001b[33m  [H8-03] \u001b[0m\u001b[1mSubagent overuse (many Task spawns)\u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Г—1\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m  frequency signal вЂ” not scored (1 calls; check context)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  fix: \u001b[0mDelegate only exploration / large independent / parallelizable work. Do simple edits and known-context queries on the main thread.\r\n\r\n\u001b[2mв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m  Total estimated waste: ~109,100 tokens\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[36m  Share: I was wasting ~42% of my Claude Code tokens. Top leak: Inviting verbose output. вЂ” tokenhabit\u001b[0m\r\n"]
